snippet.title: RED SNAPPER FISH | Big Fish Grill Recipe Cooking in Village | Fish Fry in Clay | Ancient Cooking
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook fish recipe using big red snapper fish. We grill this fish using clay. First, we apply the hand-ground traditional masala on the fish then we wrap it with banana leaf and silver foil paper and finally we cover the fish with clay. We directly grill the fish in the fire. 

Finally, we tasted the fish with a nice aroma! Tate is yummy!

snippet.title: Kya Kashmir Me Khilega Kamal? ft. Medha | Kashmir Elections | Jist
snippet.description:
In this compelling video, Jist reporter Medha travels across Anantnag, Pulwama, Baramulla, and other key areas in Kashmir to uncover the ground realities as the region prepares to vote after nearly a decade.

With the political landscape shifting dramatically, Medha highlights the significance of these elections in shaping the future of Jammu and Kashmir.

Anantnag, a stronghold of the PDP and the Mufti family, is witnessing fierce competition. 

Mehbooba Mufti's daughter, Sana, is contesting from Bijbehara while NC's Dr. Bashir Ahmad Veeri and BJP's Sofi Yousuf are also in the race. Medha captures the sentiments of local voters and the pressing issues they face.

Join us as we delve into the heart of Kashmir’s electoral dynamics and explore how these elections could redefine political alliances and governance in the region. #KashmirElection #Article370 #JammuElection #NC #PDP #OmarAbdullah #Mehboobamufti #BJP #EngineerRashid

hilal ahmad shah of apni party

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 51 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 16th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Why 40% WORLD POPULATION Live in Only 2 Countries
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo to simplify your Business - https://www.odoo.com/r/yQYN

In terms of population, India and China alone have more people than the combined total of all other 170 countries on Earth!  The world seems very crowded, and many experts suggest we need to control population growth. Even Elon Musk is talking about moving to Mars because of this issue.
However, if you look at the world population map, you'll see that most of the planet is still uninhabited. In Asia, India and China together house 2.7 billion people, or 36% of the world’s population. So, why do these two countries, located on the same continent, hold such a significant portion of the global population? Is their geographical location a key factor? Let's discuss.

Kaffara Episode 50 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 15th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: VENOM: THE LAST DANCE - New Hindi Trailer | In Cinemas October 25
snippet.description:
With you to the end.

Witness the epic conclusion in #Venom: The Last Dance - exclusively in cinemas on October 25. Releasing in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu.

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel’s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.

snippet.description:
ഞാൻ കുറച്ച് നാളായി ഒരു ഫീൽ ഗുഡ് സിനിമ ചെയ്തിട്ട്. എന്റെ ഉള്ളിൽ നന്മ ഉണ്ടായില്ല. 'കഥ ഇന്നുവരെ' ഒരു പ്രോപ്പർ ഫീൽ ഗുഡ് സിനിമയാണ്. 
ഓൺലൈൻ മീഡിയ മാത്രമല്ല സാറ്റ്ലൈറ്റ് ചാനലും ഇപ്പോൾ പ്രഹസനമാണ് കാണിക്കുന്നത്. എന്നെ തഗ് എന്ന് മീഡിയ വിളിക്കുന്നതാണ്. ഞാൻ മറുപടിയാണ് പറയുന്നത്. ക്യു സ്റ്റുഡിയോയിൽ നിഖില വിമലും ഹക്കീം ഷാജഹാനും 

Nikhila Vimal and Hakim Shajahan speaks about their new movie 'Kadha Innuvare'. Nikhila shares her opinion about online media, why she has a thug image and how online media hinders the privacy of actors. Hakim Shajahan adds onto this about how his marriage function got affected with the intervention of media.

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Highlights | Australia Tour Of England | 13th September 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-australia-tour-of-england-1700001523

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

In the 2nd T20I, England won the toss and elected to bowl first. Australia posted 193 runs with the loss of 6 wickets in 20 overs. Jake Fraser-McGurk was the top scorer with a terrific knock of 50 from 31 balls. Later, Australian bowlers troubled England batters and kept on taking wickets. England lost 2 wickets in quick succession but Liam Livingstone kept the hopes alive for his team scoring 87 runs in 47 balls, England won the match by 3 wickets and tied the 3 match series 1-1.

snippet.title: 1st T20I | Highlights | Australia Tour Of England | 11th September 2024
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, England won the toss and elected to bowl first. Australia posted 179 runs and became all out by 19.3 overs. Travis Head was the top scorer with a terrific knock of 59 from 23 balls. Later, Australian bowlers troubled England batters and kept on taking wickets. England lost all 10 wickets for 151 runs as Australia sealed a 28-run win in the end.
.

snippet.title: ആരാണ് കാട്ടിലെ ഏറ്റവും അക്രമകാരി, മുന്നിൽപെട്ടാൽ എങ്ങനെ രക്ഷപ്പെടാം I Service story of a Naturalist
snippet.description:
കരടിക്കു മുന്നില്‍ ചത്ത പോലെ കിടന്നാല്‍ രക്ഷപ്പെടുമെന്ന കഥ ചെറുപ്പം മുതല്‍ നമ്മളെല്ലാം കേട്ടു ശീലിച്ചിട്ടുള്ളതാണ്. പക്ഷെ എത്രത്തോളം യുക്തിപരമാണ് ആ കഥ. അതുപോലെ മറ്റൊന്നാണ് കരടിക്ക് തേനിനോടുള്ള പ്രിയമെന്നത്. ശരിക്കും കരടിയെ ആകര്‍ഷിക്കുന്നത് തേനോ അതോ അതിനുള്ളിലെ ലാര്‍വകളോ. കാട്ടിലെ രസകരമായ അനുഭവങ്ങൾ, വന്യജീവി ആക്രമണങ്ങൾ, കൗതുമുണർത്തുന്ന ജീവികൾ, ഓരോ ജീവികളുടെയും വ്യത്യസ്തതരം ഇരതേടൽ രീതികൾ, കാടും വന്യജീവികളുമായി ബന്ധപ്പെട്ട മിഥ്യാധാരണകൾ എന്നിവയെക്കുറിച്ചെല്ലാം സംസാരിക്കുകയാണ്  .  ഇത്തവണ service storyൽ നാച്ചറലിസ്റ്റും എഴുത്തുകാരനുമായ ഡേവിഡ് രാജുവിന്റെ കാടനുഭവങ്ങൾ കേൾക്കാം
